            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Once hot, add the <strong>haddock bites</strong> and <strong>sliced garlic</strong> cook for 5 min, turning once half way, or until cooked through and crispy – this is your <strong>pan-fried haddock</strong></p><p>Tip: Your fish is cooked once it turns opaque and flakes easily</p>",
